Steps to reproduce:

- Create a word document in any .doc or .docx format with any content;
- Insert an image on it;
- Create a new page confluence with any title;
- Attach the previously document;
- Use the following macro: {viewdoc:name=MyDocument.docx}
- You'll be able to visualize correctly the content;
- Now use the option "Export to PDF";

